Airgain
FWA Easy Installation Kit
Simpler Installation, Seamless Connectivity.
Designed with user experience at its core, this innovative outdoor antenna installation solution combines aesthetics, usability, and functionality. Featuring an installation support net and a quick-release structure, it enables effortless operation when searching for the best signal, significantly simplifying the installation process. Crafted with durable materials and optimized for stability, it delivers an intuitive and reliable user experience. Dramatically improving installation efficiency and reducing hassle, especially in complex environments, this product redefines the standards for outdoor antenna installations.
Client
Gemtek
Year
2022
Designer
Joel Chang
